00:05:35.710 --> 00:05:37.820
See this image here.

00:05:37.820 --> 00:05:42.970
100 years ago, if you told
people that you might willingly

00:05:42.970 --> 00:05:45.940
get on a bike that's had
its back wheel removed,

00:05:45.940 --> 00:05:48.010
