00:09:42.109 --> 00:09:43.900
And part of the reason
is because we're not

00:09:43.900 --> 00:09:46.180
at the same level as we are
with regard to an evidence

00:09:46.180 --> 00:09:49.810
base regarding what
you should do in order

00:09:49.810 --> 00:09:52.240
to stay psychologically fit.

00:09:52.240 --> 00:09:54.767
And what mental
exercises you should do.

00:09:54.767 --> 00:09:56.350
And that's sort of
the project of what

00:09:56.350 --> 00:09:59.620
we're talking about with regard
to the science of mindfulness.

00:09:59.620 --> 00:10:02.680
It's really to
systematically and rigorously

00:10:02.680 --> 00:10:06.094
be able to ask this question to
see what role it has to play.

00:10:06.094 --> 00:10:07.510
Now, it's not only
scientists that

00:10:07.510 --> 00:10:10.207
are interested in understanding
the answer to this question.

00:10:10.207 --> 00:10:12.040
Of course, the National
Institutes of Health

00:10:12.040 --> 00:10:13.930
