So you mentioned there
is different trainings

00:54:16.385 --> 00:54:17.970
in different studies.

00:54:17.970 --> 00:54:20.100
From a practical
perspective, what

00:54:20.100 --> 00:54:22.675
is the threshold you are looking
right now when, I guess--

00:54:22.675 --> 00:54:23.800
AMISHI JHA: Great question.

00:54:23.800 --> 00:54:25.860
AUDIENCE: --meditation
actually seems to matter?

00:54:25.860 --> 00:54:26.690
AMISHI JHA: Yeah.

00:54:26.690 --> 00:54:27.660
AUDIENCE: What's
the minimum number?

00:54:27.660 --> 00:54:28.110
AMISHI JHA: Thank you.

00:54:28.110 --> 00:54:30.090
So the question was
regarding threshold, right?

00:54:30.090 --> 00:54:32.760
So it's kind of one of those
cut to the chase things.

00:54:32.760 --> 00:54:35.340
Do I have to go on a three-month
