00:56:23.466 --> 00:56:24.840
And I just want
to say, thank you

00:56:24.840 --> 00:56:26.760
so much for doing this work.

00:56:26.760 --> 00:56:29.172
And thank you for coming
here to share it with us.

00:56:29.172 --> 00:56:30.630
AMISHI JHA: It's
my great pleasure.

00:56:30.630 --> 00:56:32.670
Thank you.

